StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetCandidateLegalO.enseByID]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
(@CandidateLegalO.enseID int)
AS
SELECT clo.[CandidateLegalO.enseId] ,clo.[PersonId] ,clo.[LegalO.enseId] ,clo.[Detail] ,clo.[IsGuilty] ,clo.[IsJuvenile] ,clo.[WaiverOccasionId] ,clo.[SubmitDate] ,lo.[LegalO.enseTypeId] FROM [usmc].[CandidateLegalO.ense] clo WITH (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN [usmc].[LegalO.ense] lo ON clo.[CandidateLegalO.enseId] = @CandidateLegalO.enseID AND clo.LegalO.enseId = lo.LegalO.enseId
